quran[6{c,v,t}:
7,138,"bani Israel ko hum ne samandar se guzaar diya, phir woh chalay aur rastay mein aik aisi qoum par unn ka guzar howa jo apne chand buton ki garweedah bani hui thi kehnay lagey,"" ae moose, hamaray liye bhi koi aisa mabood bana day jaisay inn logon ke mabood hain"" moose ne kaha"" tum log barri nadani ki baatein karte ho"
7,139,"yeh log jis tareeqa ki pairwi kar rahay hain woh to barbaad honay wala hai aur jo amal woh kar rahay hain woh sara sar baatil hai """
7,140,"phir moose ne kaha"" kya mein Allah ke siwa koi aur mabood tumahray liye talaash karoon? halaank woh Allah hi hai jis ne tumhe duniya bhar ki qomon par fazeelat bakhsh hai"
7,141,"aur ( Allah farmata hai ) woh waqt yaad karo jab hum ne firaon walon se tumhe nijaat di jin ka haal yeh tha ke tumhe sakht azaab mein mubtala rakhtay thay, tumahray beiton ko qatal karte aur tumhari aurton ko zindah rehne dete thay aur is mein tumahray rab ki taraf se tumhari barri azmaish thi"
7,142,"hum ne moose ko tees shab o roz ke liye ( koh seena par ) talab kya aur baad mein das din ka aur izafah kar diya, iss terhan uss ke rab ki muqarrar kardah muddat poooray chalees din ho gayi moose ne chaltay hue apne bhai haroon se kaha ke"" mere peechay tum meri qoum mein meri janshini karna aur theek kaam karte rehna aur bigaar peda karne walon ke tareeqay par nah chalna """
7,143,"jab woh hamaray muqarrar kiye hue waqt par pouncha aur is ke rab ne is se kalaam kya to is ne iltija ki ke"" ae rab, mujhe ya-ra-ay nazar day ke mein tujhe daikhon"" farmaya"" to mujhe nahi dekh sakta haan zara samnay ke pahar ki taraf dekh, agar woh apni jagah qaim reh jaye to Albata to mujhe dekh sakay ga"" chunancha is ke rab ne jab pahar par tajallii ki to usay rezah rezah kar diya aur moose ghash kha kar gir para jab hosh aaya to bola"" pak hai teri zaat, mein tairay huzoor tauba karta hon aur sab se pehla imaan laane wala mein hon """
